.Dd August 29, 2011
.Dt DEVPUBD 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm devpubd
.Nd device publish daemon for automatic device node creation
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl f
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
listens on
.Xr drvctl 4
for new devices and creates their device nodes using
.Xr MAKEDEV 8
if they are missing.
.Pp
When
.Fl f
is specified,
.Nm
does not go into the background.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr drvctl 8 ,
.Xr MAKEDEV 8
